---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import Header from '../../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../../components/Footer.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Privacy Policy — wordcountergo.com"
  description="Privacy policy for wordcountergo.com. Learn how we protect your data. Our word counter processes all text locally in your browser — nothing is sent to any server."
  keywords="privacy policy, word counter privacy, free word counter privacy, online word counter privacy, data privacy, wordcountergo privacy"
>
  <Header />

  <main id="main-content" aria-label="Main content" class="mx-auto max-w-[900px] px-4 sm:px-6 pt-16 sm:pt-24 pb-16 sm:pb-32">
    <div class="text-center mb-16">
      <span class="inline-flex items-center px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full bg-canvas-soft text-caption text-body font-mono uppercase tracking-wider mb-4 border border-hairline">Legal</span>
      <h1 class="text-display-xl max-sm:text-[28px] max-sm:leading-[34px] sm:text-[56px] sm:leading-[56px] font-semibold tracking-[-2.4px] text-ink">Privacy Policy.</h1>
      <p class="mt-3 text-body-lg text-body max-w-lg mx-auto">Last updated: January 2025</p>
    </div>

    <div class="space-y-8 text-body-md text-body leading-relaxed">
      <section>
        <h2 class="text-display-sm font-semibold tracking-[-0.6px] text-ink mb-3">1. Introduction</h2>
        <p>wordcountergo.com ("we", "our", "us") is committed to protecting your privacy. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and safeguard your information when you use our word counter tool and website at <a href="/" class="text-link hover:text-link-deep transition-colors">wordcountergo.com</a>.</p>
        <p class="mt-3">Our word counter is designed with privacy as a core principle. All text processing happens entirely in your browser using JavaScript. <strong>Your text never leaves your device.</strong> We do not store, transmit, or have access to any text you paste, type, or upload into the word counter tool.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-display-sm font-semibold tracking-[-0.6px] text-ink mb-3">2. Information We Collect</h2>
        <p>We collect minimal information to operate and improve our website:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mt-2 space-y-1">
          <li><strong>Usage Data:</strong> Anonymous page view statistics collected via our hosting provider to understand which pages are visited.</li>
          <li><strong>Local Storage:</strong> We use your browser's local storage to save your theme preference (dark/light mode), language selection, and the text you were working on. This data stays on your device and is never sent to our servers.</li>
          <li><strong>Google Fonts:</strong> When you load our website, your browser may request fonts from Google Fonts servers, which may collect your IP address. See <a href="https://policies.google.com/privacy" class="text-link hover:text-link-deep transition-colors" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank">Google's Privacy Policy</a> for details.</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-display-sm font-semibold tracking-[-0.6px] text-ink mb-3">3. Information We Do NOT Collect</h2>
        <p>We want to be completely transparent about what we do not collect:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mt-2 space-y-1">
          <li>We do <strong>not</strong> collect or store any text you enter into the word counter.</li>
          <li>We do <strong>not</strong> use cookies for tracking or advertising.</li>
          <li>We do <strong>not</strong> have user accounts, so we never collect names, emails, or passwords.</li>
          <li>We do <strong>not</strong> use third-party analytics services like Google Analytics.</li>
          <li>We do <strong>not</strong> sell, rent, or share any personal information.</li>
          <li>We do <strong>not</strong> use tracking pixels or fingerprinting technologies.</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-display-sm font-semibold tracking-[-0.6px] text-ink mb-3">4. How We Use Your Information</h2>
        <p>The limited information we collect is used solely for:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mt-2 space-y-1">
          <li>Providing and maintaining the word counter service.</li>
          <li>Improving website performance and user experience.</li>
          <li>Remembering your preferences (theme, language) between visits.</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-display-sm font-semibold tracking-[-0.6px] text-ink mb-3">5. Data Storage and Security</h2>
        <p>Your text is stored only in your browser's local storage if you choose to save it. This data remains on your device and can be cleared at any time by clearing your browser's local data. We implement industry-standard security measures to protect our website, though no internet transmission is 100% secure.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-display-sm font-semibold tracking-[-0.6px] text-ink mb-3">6. Third-Party Services</h2>
        <p>Our website uses the following third-party services:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mt-2 space-y-1">
          <li><strong>Google Fonts:</strong> Used for typography. Google may collect your IP address when loading fonts. See <a href="https://policies.google.com/privacy" class="text-link hover:text-link-deep transition-colors" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank">Google's Privacy Policy</a>.</li>
          <li><strong>Cloudflare:</strong> Our hosting and CDN provider. Cloudflare may process anonymized traffic data. See <a href="https://www.cloudflare.com/privacypolicy/" class="text-link hover:text-link-deep transition-colors" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank">Cloudflare's Privacy Policy</a>.</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-display-sm font-semibold tracking-[-0.6px] text-ink mb-3">7. Children's Privacy</h2>
        <p>Our service is available to all users, including children. We do not knowingly collect personal information from any user, regardless of age. As all text processing is done locally, no user data is transmitted to our servers.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-display-sm font-semibold tracking-[-0.6px] text-ink mb-3">8. Changes to This Policy</h2>
        <p>We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. Changes will be posted on this page with an updated "Last updated" date. We encourage you to review this policy periodically.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-display-sm font-semibold tracking-[-0.6px] text-ink mb-3">9. Contact Us</h2>
        <p>If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy, please <a href="/contact" class="text-link hover:text-link-deep transition-colors">contact us</a>.</p>
      </section>
    </div>
  </main>

  <Footer />
</BaseLayout>
